                     <interp inst="t17790217-16-off86" type="offenceSubcategory" value="theftFromPlace"></interp>
               stealing a silver watch, value 3 l. the property of 
                     <persName id="t17790217-16-person161">
                        Micheal
                         Hinde
                     <interp inst="t17790217-16-person161" type="surname" value="Hinde"></interp>
